    "html" :
    
    
    "Ultra-high-strength steel panels are extremely strong and rigid. These body parts are recast warm during manufacturing and are press-hardened in cooled recast tools. Damaged or deformed body parts can impair torsional rigidity, flexional resistance and crash safety. "
    
